data.description: ***ASSUMABLE LOAN @ 4.25% FHA**** Let's admit that Location is vital for someone looking for a home in San Antonio Texas. Are you looking to enroll in the Northside Independent School District? Is it because SeaWorld is approximately 3 miles away or six flags & The Shops of LaCantera are 14 miles away? Could it be that the heart of Downtown Riverwalk is 15 miles south! This neighborhood boasts the ease of highway access, shopping to HEB/ Walmart /The Home Depot/ Target/ Starbucks/ Gold's gym. The owner's suite can fit a king size bed.  The backyard is big to place a shed or play area. Check out this home today.
